>> [`` \frac{\partial }{\partial x}([$f])={}``][___________]*{$dfx} <<

>> [`` \frac{\partial }{\partial y}([$f])={}``][___________]*{$dfy} <<

>> [`` \frac{\partial }{\partial x}([$g])={}``][___________]*{$dgx} <<

>> [`` \frac{\partial }{\partial y}([$g])={}``][___________]*{$dgy} <<

---------------

